OL,3,CStarmer urges US and Iran 'to find a
OL,4,Cway through' after peace talks fail
OL,6,FThe Prime Minister, Sir Keir Starmer,
OL,7,Fhas urged the US and Iran "to find a
OL,8,Fway through" after the failure of
OL,9,Fpeace talks, as he also called for the
OL,10,Ffragile ceasefire to continue and
OL,11,Fwarned against any further escalation.
OL,13,FThe Prime Minister discussed
OL,14,FWashington and Tehran's negotiations
OL,15,Fwith the Sultan of Oman after the two
OL,16,Fsides' 21-hour session in Pakistan
OL,17,Fended without an agreement in the
OL,18,Fearly hours of Sunday.
OL,26,@oD@[OUpD@LO]
