OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776017467
OL,3,CStarmer urges US and Iran 'to find a
OL,4,Cway through' after peace talks fail
OL,6,FUS Vice-President JD Vance left
OL,7,FIslamabad without a deal, pointing to
OL,8,FIran's refusal to commit to not
OL,9,Fbuilding a nuclear weapon, leaving
OL,10,Funcertainty over the shaky two-week
OL,11,Ftruce.
OL,13,FIn a readout of Starmer's call with
OL,14,FHis Majesty Sultan Haitham bin Tarik
OL,15,Fal Said, a Downing Street spokeswoman
OL,16,Fsaid: "They discussed the peace talks
OL,17,Fheld in Pakistan over the weekend and
OL,18,Furged both sides to find a way through.
OL,26,@xD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
