OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776017467
OL,3,CStarmer urges US and Iran 'to find a
OL,4,Cway through' after peace talks fail
OL,6,F"It was vital there was a continuation
OL,7,Fof the ceasefire, and that all parties
OL,8,Favoided any further escalation, the
OL,9,Fleaders agreed."
OL,11,FThey also discussed efforts to reopen
OL,12,Fthe vital Strait of Hormuz oil and gas
OL,13,Fshipping lane, which has been
OL,14,Feffectively closed by Iran's grip,
OL,15,Fsending energy prices soaring.
OL,17,FBritain will host further talks on
OL,18,Freopening the maritime pinch-point
OL,19,Fwith a coalition of countries next
OL,20,Fweek.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@PO]
