OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FAccording to the call readout: "His
OL,12,Fmajesty updated on the situation in
OL,13,Fthe Strait of Hormuz, and the prime
OL,14,Fminister thanked him for Oman's
OL,15,Fefforts to rescue sailors from vessels
OL,16,Fin distress in the region.
OL,26,@sD@`OU
