OL,3,CStarmer urges US and Iran 'to find a
OL,4,Cway through' after peace talks fail
OL,6,F"Reflecting on international efforts
OL,7,Fto coordinate safe passage for
OL,8,Fshipping in the region, the prime
OL,9,Fminister said that following meetings
OL,10,Fconvened by the Foreign Secretary and
OL,11,FBritish military planners, partners
OL,12,Fcontinued to work towards restoring
OL,13,Ffreedom of navigation for the long
OL,14,Fterm."
OL,16,FThe prime minister visited allies in
OL,17,Fthe Gulf this week for talks on how to
OL,18,Fsupport what he described as a
OL,19,F"fragile" ceasefire.
